## Revenue trend

```chart type=line data=sales x=month y=revenue series=region points title="Monthly revenue by region"
```

## Regional breakdown

```chart type=bar x=region y=total title="Total Q1 revenue by region"
region, total
North, 595
South, 475
East, 360
West, 635
```

## Product mix

```chart type=pie label=product value=share donut title="Product mix"
product, share
Alpha, 45
Beta, 30
Gamma, 15
Delta, 10
```

